data.description: Beautiful home with a new steel roof, on a large lot, decks for entertainment on front and back, large open kitchen, high ceilings, and a fireplace in the family room. Master En Suite is large, with a great bathroom, soaking tub, double vanity and 2 walk in closets. Lot is covered with trees. *** CHECK OUT THE TAX RATE ONLY 1.683%, you can't beat that!!  NO HOA BRING YOUR RV OR BOAT, OR BOTH :)  Truly a must see.
